videos.description: Hayden Moore's pass is intercepted by UConn's Marshe Terry in the end zone and returned for 6 yards.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Moore throws INT in red zone

videos.description: Connecticut's David Pindell's pass is picked off by Hunter Jacobs and returned for 21 yards.
videos.headline: Pindell's INT gives Cincinnati good field position

videos.description: Hayden Moore delivers a 13-yard touchdown pass to Kahlil Lewis in the end zone to put the Bearcats ahead 7-6 just before halftime.
videos.headline: Lewis makes nice grab for Cincinnati TD

videos.description: David Pindell sneaks into the end zone for a touchdown, but the Huskies failed to convert a 2-point conversion.
videos.headline: Pindell's short rushing TD puts UConn ahead

videos.description: Hayden Moore finds Kahlil Lewis in the end zone for a touchdown and converts the 2-point play to tie the score at 15-15 early in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Cincinnati ties it up with TD and 2-pt conversion

videos.description: Hayden Moore keeps the football and runs 4 yards to the house to put the Bearcats ahead 22-15 with under two-minutes remaining in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Moore's rushing TD puts Cincinnati back on top

videos.description: David Pindell delivers a long pass to Quayvon Skanes for the UConn 1st down with less than one minute to go in the game.
videos.headline: Pindell's 34-yard pass gives UConn one last chance
